<HEAD>First Pet Cemetery in Hungary Opens in Fall</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BUDAPEST, Hungary (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Hungary's first pet cemetery will open
this fall after the necessary permits are issued to the private
group that will run it, a government newspaper reported Thursday.
   The last resting place for the ``loved ones'' is being
established by the Rakosvoelgye cooperative farm, ``true to the
